{"tid":1004594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德州少女街頭自慰呻吟　遭押上警車仲繼續亂摸.  冇圖","createTime":"2019-02-01T14:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T15:37:39.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e47475b935a36dc72f1e2fef7889fa5dba1e13d5","tid":1004594,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:20:51.000Z","msg":"美國德州奧斯汀一名女子，周二（1月29日）手持一件銀色物體，半裸地站在街頭張開雙腿自慰，期間不斷發出呻吟聲，情況持續近8分鐘。附近酒店職員報案，警員到場將女子帶走。未知女子是否意猶未盡，她被鎖上手銬後，竟繼續在警車上自慰，令人側目。 <br />\n<br />\n26歲女子尼科爾斯（Dovie Nickels）當日下午在奧斯汀JW萬豪酒店附近自慰，酒店職員隨即上前阻止，但尼科爾斯未有理會，並轉移陣地到別處繼續。期間尼科爾斯如入無人之境，在一間酒吧內任意高聲呻吟，令途人非常尷尬。 <br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場後，發現尼科爾斯下身沒穿褲，隨即將她鎖上手銬，並帶上警車。詎料女子竟然在警車上繼續自慰。她被控不雅裸露罪名，保釋金為3,000美元（約2.3萬港元）。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190201/mobile/bkn-20190201094623073-0201_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190201%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190201094623073-0201_00972_001.html&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxspNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=1f934b38\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190201/mobile/bkn-20190201094623073-0201_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190201/photo/bkn-20190201094623073-0201_00972_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190201094623073-0201_00972_001_02p.jpg&h=31c51181&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82f6401b040300a065a0bdcd82ff8cef2a950acd","tid":1004594,"uid":220236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:22:30.000Z","msg":"警察會唔會聽到扯晒"},{"pid":"fd936aa620d0146f4c54d3a476407301370fb387","tid":1004594,"uid":40226,"like":16,"dislike":